# blaventure
# version 0.4 
#
# patch notes [30/09/2015]
#

*General*

*NEW*
- Added a shop encounter
	- Shops will sometimes be encountered in the wilds now
	- Can sell potions, tents, and equipment

- Gold rewards have increased significantly
	- You will receive a lot more money than previously
	- The shop has been balanced with this in mind
